data.name: LeBron James Autographed & Inscribed Game-Used Nike LeBron 11 Shoes (vs. Nuggets 3/14/14), 1 of 1
data.description: Here is a unique opportunity to own a pair of game-used basketball shoes from one of the greatest basketball players to ever lace up a pair of high tops. LeBron James autographed and inscribed these white, black and red Nike LeBron 11 shoes from the 2014 season with the Miami Heat. This pair of shoes was worn by James during his record-setting run in South Beach. This 1-of-1 pair has been autographed on the right shoe with a hand-written inscription on the left. They were worn in a game against the Denver Nuggets on 3/14/14 in which James scored 21 points with six rebounds and six assists and three steals in a 111-107 home loss. The Heat went on to make their fourth consecutive NBA Finals appearance that season, falling just short of winning their third straight title. James has autographed and inscribed “vs. Nuggets 3/14/14” on this limited edition (1) pair of game-used Nike shoes in black paint pen. His signature is deemed authentic by virtue of Upper Deck Authenticated’s Five-Step Process.

data.description: Humble Beginnings The world has dramatically changed since 1974 when Elaine Coyne and a small staff started a collectible artwear business in a small studio in downtown Boston. We packed up our creative art line and wrote orders with pen and paper. We handed one piece of paper to the gallery owner and another to the salesperson who represented our arty cuffs, original earrings, limited edition necklaces and designer belts, which in turn gave us permission to ship the gallery in a timely manner. The reorder level was generally a week to one month. We became an established go-to company for galleries and better boutiques nationally. It was very exciting.

data.name: Bell & Ross BR 05 Rose Gold Automatic Watch
data.description: The BR05 collection draws design inspiration from Bell & Ross's earlier BR01 and BR03 models, which were influenced by aircraft cockpit instruments. Like its predecessors, BR05 features large lume-treated hands, Arabic numerals, and a round dial framed within a square case with rounded corners. Notably, BR05 flips the design by placing the rounded-corner square as the bezel instead of the case body, while maintaining elements like the numeral typeface and the four prominent screws. It houses the BR-CAL.321 movement, based on the Sellita SW-300 caliber.

data.description: The Off-White x Nike Dunk Low “University Gold” is one of three exclusive colorways of Virgil Abloh’s remixing of the classic sneaker. A University Gold leather base covers the toe, mid-panel and ankle collar. Navy leather overlays contrast the bright yellow panels on the forefoot, toe, eyelets, and heel with navy Swoosh branding located on the mid-panel. Traditional blue laces appear where they have always been, though Abloh opts to add a second set of bright orange laces in a staggered fashion throughout the upper. Completing the look of the limited collaboration is a white rubber midsole with a blue outsole.

data.name: LLADRÓ an Afternoon Nap Mother Figurine. Porcelain Mother Figure.
data.description: HANDMADE IN SPAIN: The highest-quality pieces handcrafted in Valencia, in the only LLADRÓ factory in the world. A team of expert artists and designers keep alive ancestral trades and techniques to turn porcelain into dreams. Sculptors, ornamenters, technicians, painters are all involved in the craftsmanship process... An endless number of hands that, one by one, leave their mark, an almost imperceptible imprint, making each artwork UNIQUE and EXCLUSIVE. BEAUTY AND SUSTAINABILITY: Our goal is always to create beauty from a place of sustainability and respect, principles that are part of the brand’s DNA. Lladró respects all the resources involved in the process of creating, making and selling our porcelain artworks, to offer a BEAUTIFUL, SUSTAINABLE and DURABLE product. QUALITY AND EXCELLENCE: The pursuit of perfection is not only part of the process of designing and creating the pieces, but also extends to quality control, where the finished SCULPTURE undergoes various tests to certify that it meets Lladró’s high self-imposed standards. Excellence is also applied to the packaging, which is customised to the particularities of each piece, so that it reaches its final destination safely and in PERFECT condition. A GIFT THAT WILL LAST A LIFETIME: The finest details come in the form of porcelain. Gifting a LLADRÓ artwork is synonymous with celebration and joy. It’s a way of saying: I love you, I am happy for your success or welcome. We have the perfect piece for every SPECIAL OCCASION, thanks to a wide range of artistic creations that your loved ones will value and treasure forever. LLADRÓ: Founded in 1953, Lladró is the result of three brothers’ passion for PORCELAIN; Juan, José and Vicente Lladró. Over the years, the expressive possibilities of porcelain have been pushed to the limit, reaching its own unique and distinctive style, which has given the company international fame.

data.name: Zimbabwe - 100 Trillion Dollars Collectible Banknote - Uncirculated
data.description: This unique banknote from Zimbabwe makes a fascinating collectible. Issued in 2008 during a time of hyperinflation, it bears the enormous denomination of 100 trillion dollars. Still in uncirculated condition, the note displays the national bird of Zimbabwe, along with intricate security features to confirm its authenticity. Individually packaged in a clear sleeve and rigid mailer, it has been carefully preserved for collection or display. A quirky reminder of an economic crisis, this certified gem of a note would be a conversation starter in any numismatist's collection. Examine the fine details of the note through the clear packaging to appreciate its near-pristine quality and historic significance from a remarkable period in Zimbabwe's history.

data.name: Michael Jordan & Serena Williams Autographed Red & Black Nike Court Flare Air Jordan1 Shoes - Upper Deck - Tennis Autographed Miscellaneous Items
data.description: Serena Williams shares many things in common with Michael Jordan, the chief of which is their unending pursuit to be a champion. So when Williams captured her 23rd career Grand Slam singles title at the 2017 Australian Open, it was MJ who surprised Serena with a custom edition of the Nike Court Air Jordans. Serena actually wore the red and black ones at the trophy ceremony following her victory. These shoes made specifically to honor the shared legendary status symbolizing Jordan's famous jersey number and Williams' win that tied the all-time mark held by Margaret Court. Friends in life and in legacy, both legends have autographed this pair of shoes for a truly unique memorabilia item. Jordan and Williams have autographed these limited edition (23) red and black Nike Court Flare Air Jordan1 shoes in silver paint pen. Their signatures are on the right shoe and are deemed authentic by virtue of Upper Deck Authenticated's Five-Step Process. If a product is unsigned or non game-used, a hologram will not be included Michael Jordan memorabilia. memorabilia

data.name: Celestron Advanced VX 8" EdgeHD Telescope - with Deluxe Accessory Kit (5 Celestron Plossl Eyepieces, 1.25" Barlow Lens, 1.25" Filter Set, Accessory Carry Case
data.description: Celestron Advanced VX 8" EdgeHD: truly the ultimate entry-level astroimaging package. This package combines the groundbreaking new Advanced VXmount with Celestron's best optics, the EdgeHD optical system. This setup offers the astroimager maximum versatility allowing up to 3 different f-stop configurations. Users can attach a camera to the rear of the telescope and shoot at f/10, or attach our 8-inchfocal reducer (coming soon) and shoot at f/7. Additionally, EdgeHD is Fastar/Hyperstar compatible, giving imagers the option to shoot at ultra-fast f/2. No matter which configuration you choose, EdgeHD technology gives you pinpoint stars all the way to the edge of the CCD sensor. With an 8-inch optical tube and our portable Advanced VX mount, this setup can be easily transported and assembled by one person. You'll also have plenty of load capacity to attach your camera and other accessories. This setup is simple enough for a beginner to use, but can also provide years of enjoyment for sophisticated astroimagers. About the Mount The new Advanced VX mount was specifically designed to provide optimum imaging performance for smaller telescopes. Now your smaller telescope can take advantage of All-Star Polar Alignment and autoguider support. You'll be able to track through long exposures using permanently programmable periodic error correction. Image across the meridian without doing a meridian flip, so you can seamlessly image the best part of night sky. Advance
